wdi-BX.GSR.CCIS.CD.def: Information and communication technology service exports include computer and communications services (telecommunications and postal and courier services) and information services (computer data and news-related service transactions). Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BX.GSR.CCIS.CD.name: ICT service exports
wdi-BX.GSR.CCIS.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
